                      Contact Us
                    

For customer service, please email:
 customersupport@affiniongroup.com
For help with Insurance policies:
If you are an individual who is enrolled in coverage and would like to make changes or update your information, please call our Customer Contact Center 1-800-252-2148 or email us at customerserviceinsurance@affiniongroup.com. 
Please have your policy ID number available. You can find that information on your billing statement.
If you are a client (or would like to be) please email:
 clientsupport@affiniongroup.com
For Media requests, please email:
 media@affiniongroup.com
For Investor Relations requests, please email:
 investorrelations@affiniongroup.com
