                BBB Rating Scorecard
            






Overview


Affinion Group, Inc. offers membership, insurance and loyalty products through automatic renewal subscription programs including credit monitoring and identity theft resolution services, as well as online discount programs for retail merchandise, travel, automotive and home improvement.

 












