			Company Description 


			Affinion Group Holdings, Inc. engages in the designing, marketing, and servicing of customer engagement and loyalty solutions. It operates through the following segments: Membership Products, Insurance and Package Products, Global Loyalty Products, and International Products. The Membership Products...
		


                Affinion Group Holdings, Inc. engages in the designing, marketing, and servicing of customer engagement and loyalty solutions. It operates through the following segments: Membership Products, Insurance and Package Products, Global Loyalty Products, and International Products. The Membership Products segment involves in designing, implementing, and marketing subscription program. The Insurance and Package Products segment offers designing and providing checking account enhancement programs to financial institutions. The Global Loyalty Products segment includes designing, implementing, and administer points-based loyalty programs. The International Products segment comprises of membership and package customer engagement businesses. The company was founded in 1973 and is headquartered in Stamford, CT.
            




